text.tspan: Homicide rate, IHME vs. WHO Mortality Database, 2019
Homicide rate is measured as the number of intentional homicide per 100,000 inhabitants of a country or region.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019); WHO Mortality Database (2022)
